.TH "ips_disable_cpu_turbo" 9 "ips_disable_cpu_turbo" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ips_disable_cpu_turbo \- disable turbo mode on all CPUs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ips_disable_cpu_turbo
.BI "(struct ips_driver *ips "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ips" 12
IPS driver struct
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Disable turbo mode by setting the disable bit in IA32_PERF_CTL on
all logical threads.
